description:
Available for purchase at <a href="http://singerhill.com/?page_id=226" target="_blank">Singer Hill Cafe &amp; Gallery</a> Oregon City.

This is an original mixed media collage painting of a cherry blossom tree in full bloom. The background is made from real vintage dictionary pages collaged onto a black canvas. Layered over the top is a faux encaustic. A cherry blossom tree is the finishing touch.

-Cheery Blossom Tree
-Mixed Media/Collage/Painting/Canvas
-Size 11X14x.5"
-by Blenda Tyvoll

The painting is on stretched wrapped canvas with staples on the back. The edges are painted black.

This piece is artist signed on front and back. It is ready to hang on your wall unframed or if you wish you can frame it in an 11x14" frame that matches your decor.

